'''AltCar Expo''' is the [[alternative energy]] and transportation [[Trade fair|expo]] in [[Santa Monica Civic Auditorium]].
Admission is free.
In the 2008 Expo (September 26 and 27), the [[Chevrolet Volt]] prototype was seen by more than 15,000 people in Santa Monica at AltCar Expo.<ref>[http://www.calcars.org/calcars-news/1006.html CEOs & Generals Plug In; Iceland Giving Up on Hydrogen]</ref>
